    <string name="native_lib_missing_body">This APK was built without libbconet.so, so BCO cannot start the mesh engine.\n\nDevelopers: install the Android NDK (SDK Manager), then from bco-core run:\n\n  ANDROID_NDK_HOME=$ANDROID_HOME/ndk/VERSION make android-arm64\n\nCopy the library:\n\n  cp build/android-arm64/libbconet.so ../bco-shell/app/src/main/jniLibs/arm64-v8a/\n\nRebuild and reinstall the app. See bco-core/README.md and bco-shell/app/src/main/jniLibs/arm64-v8a/README.md.</string>

